Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Name",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar-updated.png",
  "birthDate": "2000-01-01T00:00:00",
  "gender": 0,
  "bio": "Updated bio"
}

### Calculate BMI
POST {{host}}/bmi/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
